text: Hi everyone! I'm Alice, the content marketing person at SEOmonitor, a SaaS company for SEO agencies. I've been a writer & researcher, comms & content person for +11 years, jumping between freelancing and full-time jobs in the last 7. Fun fact: I have a PhD in Comms Science with a thesis on anime communities and fandom in Eastern Europe. Really excited to be here, I've been learning a lot already! :star-struck:

text:
Hi Everyone :wave::skin-tone-5:, 

I’m Fadeke, a Content Marketing Manager at Doist, the team behind Todoist and Twist! Our content mostly lives on the <https://doist.com/blog/|Ambition and Balance blog>. We produce content on productivity, remote work, and team communication. We’re a fully remote team and I’m based in Edmonton, AB Canada! :flag-ca:

This community is awesome –– I’ve looked around for a while and thought it was time for a formal introduction! Looking forward to chatting and learning with you all. :blush:
